  * {{ill|Yoshizaki Gobo|ja|吉崎御坊}}
  * {{ill|Ikkō Ikki|ja|一向一揆}}
* {{ill|Senchū-ji|ja|専修寺}} ({{ill|Shinshū Takada-ha|ja|真宗高田派}})
* {{ill|Kimpusen-ji|ja|金峯山寺}} (Yoshino)
* {{ill|Kōfuku-ji|ja|興福寺}}
