* {{ill|Heisen-ji|ja|平泉寺}} (now {{ill|Heisen-ji Hakusan Shrine|ja|平泉寺白山神社}})
* {{ill|Isurugi-yama|ja|石動山}} Tenpyō-ji (now {{ill|Isurugi Hikojinja|ja|伊須流岐比古神社}})
* {{ill|Tōnomine|ja|多武峰}} Myōraku-ji (now {{ill|Tanzan Shrine|ja|談山神社}})
